		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~magzteel">magzteel</a>  <span class="uid"><a href="//slashdot.org/~magzteel">( 5013587 )</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
